IndieWebCamp Cambridge 2014

   Main article: 2014/Cambridge

   The next IndieWebCamp is in Cambridge, MA, US - one of many IndieWeb
   events.

   Own your data.

   Rather than posting content on third-party silos of content, we should
   all own the content we're creating. Publish on your own domain, and
   syndicate out to silos.

   Join us at MIT for two days of a BarCamp-style gathering of web
   creators building and sharing open web technologies to empower users to
   own their own identities & content, and advance the state of the indie
   web!
